title: THE FILE CONTAINING THE APP WAS RENAMED RoboApp; this was long overdue. I added…
message: THE FILE CONTAINING THE APP WAS RENAMED RoboApp; this was long overdue. I added a second android app to the repo, FaceTracker; this is largely for development purposes. I followed a tutorial provided by google and used some starter code to make an app that can track multiple faces, track whether each eye is open, and detect happiness based on facial markers; all of this is done in a video feed. The purpose of the app is documented in the README; however, I still need to document the smaller components of the app. Download and use the FaceTracker app, praise google for making it so easy, and I'll work on incorporating it into RoboApp.
